				Admin			</span>
			</a>
		</span>

		 / <span class="ast-taxonomy-container tags-links default"><a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/acompanyaments/" rel="tag">acompanyaments</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/amazu-zuke/" rel="tag">amazu-zuke</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/bitxo-fresc/" rel="tag">bitxo fresc</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/conservacio-en-fred/" rel="tag">conservació en fred</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/cuina-asiatica/" rel="tag">cuina asiàtica</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/cuina-japonesa/" rel="tag">cuina japonesa</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/daikon/" rel="tag">daikon</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/encurtits-casolans/" rel="tag">encurtits casolans</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/encurtits-japonesos/" rel="tag">encurtits japonesos</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/escabetxos-lleugers/" rel="tag">escabetxos lleugers</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/fermentacio-suau/" rel="tag">fermentació suau</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/fonoll/" rel="tag">fonoll</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/gingebre/" rel="tag">gingebre</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/guarnicions/" rel="tag">guarnicions</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/kombu/" rel="tag">kombu</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/nap/" rel="tag">nap</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/pastanaga/" rel="tag">pastanaga</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/receptes-japoneses/" rel="tag">receptes japoneses</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/shio-zuke/" rel="tag">shio-zuke</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/tsukemono/" rel="tag">tsukemono</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/umami/" rel="tag">umami</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/verdures-encurtides/" rel="tag">verdures encurtides</a>, <a href="https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/tag/vinagre-darros/" rel="tag">vinagre d’arròs</a></span></div>		</header><!-- .entry-header -->
					<div class="ast-excerpt-container ast-blog-single-element">
				<p>Encurtits japonesos cruixents, de guarda curta Fa temps, en un restaurant japonès, vaig descobrir els&nbsp;tsukemono&nbsp;tradicionals: verdures encurtides amb una textura sorprenentment cruixent i un sabor concentrat però net. No són escabetxos agressius ni fermentacions descontrolades, sinó una cuina de precisió, equilibri i temps. Aquesta recepta és una&nbsp;adaptació domèstica fidel a l’esperit japonès, basada en un&nbsp;pre-salat [&hellip;]</p>
<div class='sfsiaftrpstwpr'><div class='sfsi_responsive_icons' style='display:block;margin-top:10px; margin-bottom: 10px; width:100%' data-icon-width-type='Fully responsive' data-icon-width-size='240' data-edge-type='Round' data-edge-radius='5'  ><div class='sfsi_icons_container sfsi_responsive_without_counter_icons sfsi_medium_button_container sfsi_icons_container_box_fully_container ' style='width:100%;display:flex; text-align:center;' ><a target='_blank' href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcuinetes.linuxbcn.com%2F2026%2F01%2F17%2Ftsukemono-casolans-amb-vinagre-darros%2F' style='display:block;text-align:center;margin-left:10px;  flex-basis:100%;' class=sfsi_responsive_fluid ><div class='sfsi_responsive_icon_item_container sfsi_responsive_icon_facebook_container sfsi_medium_button sfsi_responsive_icon_gradient sfsi_centered_icon' style=' border-radius:5px; width:auto; ' ><img style='max-height: 25px;display:unset;margin:0' class='sfsi_wicon' alt='facebook' src='https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/responsive-icon/facebook.svg'><span style='color:#fff'>Share on Facebook</span></div></a><a target='_blank' href='https://x.com/intent/post?text=%23cuineteslinuxbcn+via%40linuxbcn&url=https%3A%2F%2Fcuinetes.linuxbcn.com%2F2026%2F01%2F17%2Ftsukemono-casolans-amb-vinagre-darros%2F' style='display:block;text-align:center;margin-left:10px;  flex-basis:100%;' class=sfsi_responsive_fluid ><div class='sfsi_responsive_icon_item_container sfsi_responsive_icon_twitter_container sfsi_medium_button sfsi_responsive_icon_gradient sfsi_centered_icon' style=' border-radius:5px; width:auto; ' ><img style='max-height: 25px;display:unset;margin:0' class='sfsi_wicon' alt='Twitter' src='https://cuinetes.linuxbcn.com/wp-content/plugins/ultimate-social-media-icons/images/responsive-icon/Twitter.svg'><span style='color:#fff'>Tweet</span></div></a><a target='_blank' href='https://api.follow.it/widgets/icon/b0taL00zSHBHbDh